snippet.title: The Front Closed Beta Test Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Closed Beta Test of The Front!
www.playthefront.com

Finish the survey and get your chance to enter the closed beta test!

Video footage was taken from the actual gameplay, and does not represent the final quality.


Wishlist now on Steam!
store.steampowered.com/app/2285150

https://store.epicgames.com/p/the-front-3a8219
